In a further aspect, the present invention provides polynucleotides that are RNA transcripts of the DNA sequences of the present invention.


Accordingly, there is provided an RNA polynucleotide that:


(a) comprises an RNA transcript of the DNA sequence encoding the polypeptide of SEQ ID NO:2;


(b) is the RNA transcript of the DNA sequence encoding the polypeptide of SEQ ID NO:2;


(c) comprises an RNA transcript of the DNA sequence of SEQ ID NO:1; or


(d) is the RNA transcript of the DNA sequence of SEQ ID NO:1; and RNA polynucleotides that are complementary thereto.

Accordingly, in a further aspect, the present invention provides for an isolated polynucleotide which:


